snippet.title: The Void Calls Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2258930/The_Void_Calls/
The Void Calls, and you will answer. Explore the mysteries and secrets of Reprieve, a town stitched together from the dark past of its bizarre inhabitants in this horror-filled point-and-click adventure. Coming soon to Steam!

Music by SnakeDere: https://twitter.com/snakedere

Twitter: https://twitter.com/slyfincleton
Itch: https://slyfincleton.itch.io/
Alternate Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAiOUmHArJvwEpSTdtnKI5w
